16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 68 O.S. 2021, Section 2357.45, is
18 amended to read as follows:
19 Section 2357.45. A. 1. For tax years beginning after December
20 31, 2004, there shall be allowed against the tax imposed by Section
21 2355 of this title, a credit for any taxpayer who makes a donation
22 to an independent biomedical research institute and for tax years
23 beginning after December 31, 2010, a credit for any taxpayer who
24 makes a donation to a cancer research institute.
